goal.tools.unittest.testsection.testconditions

Class TestConditionEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • goal.tools.unittest.testsection.testconditions.TestConditionEvaluator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DebugObserver

    public abstract class TestConditionEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
implements DebugObserver
    Base to evaluate TestConditions in the context of a running agent. The Evaluator is installed on the debugger and receives a call back whenever an action has been executed.
    Author:
    mpkorstanje
